Yeah, for a lot of private reasons.

42
00:03:01,281 --> 00:03:02,214
Kaji?

43
00:03:02,215 --> 00:03:03,948
Shut up!

44
00:03:03,950 --> 00:03:06,418
Well, how's the Third Child doing?

45
00:03:06,420 --> 00:03:07,486
Take a look.

46
00:03:07,487 --> 00:03:08,777
Let me see.

47
00:03:09,623 --> 00:03:13,659
I hope that knowing this
will boost his confidence.

48
00:03:13,660 --> 00:03:14,950
Can you hear me, Shinji?

49
