To be honest, getting beat that easily
is a little frustrating, don't you think?

53
00:03:32,212 --> 00:03:35,251
He's amazing, wonderful,
awesome, too awesome!

54
00:03:36,683 --> 00:03:38,451
The great invincible Shiniji!

55
00:03:38,452 --> 00:03:42,621
This just means we get to
take it easy now, right?

56
