What's going on? What about
the radar observation center at Fu;ji?

71
00:04:51,057 --> 00:04:54,160
They didn't detect it. It just suddenly
appeared directly above us.

72
00:04:54,161 --> 00:04:56,796
Pattern orange. No AT Field detected.

73
00:04:56,797 --> 00:04:57,730
What does that mean?

74
00:04:57,731 --> 00:04:59,064
A new kind of Angel?

75
00:04:59,065 --> 00:05:01,500
The Magi are withholding judgment.

76
00:05:01,501 --> 00:05:04,520
Damn! Commander lkari just had to be gone
at a time like this.

77
00:05:14,981 --> 00:05:16,282
Can you all hear me?

78
00:05:16,283 --> 00:05:18,684
I've sent you all of the target's data.

79
00:05:18,685 --> 00:05:21,086
That's all we know right now.

80
00:05:21,087 --> 00:05:23,556
Approach it carefully and observe its reactions,

81
00:05:23,557 --> 00:05:27,193
and, if possible, lure it into the airspace
outside of the city limits.

82
00:05:27,194 --> 00:05:30,396
One of you take point and the other two
are backup, got that?

83
00:05:30,397 --> 00:05:33,907
Ma'am?!  think Shinji ought to take point!

84
00:05:35,235 --> 00:05:39,038
Well, this is a job for the
high-scoring, utterly fearless,

85
00:05:39,039 --> 00:05:42,608
Number One synch-rate holder, right?

86
00:05:42,609 --> 00:05:44,919
Or don't you feel up to it, Shin?

87
00:05:45,779 --> 00:05:46,859
I can do it!

88
00:05:47,547 --> 00:05:49,315
I'll show you how it's done, Asuka.

89
00:05:49,316 --> 00:05:51,884
What was that?!

90
00:05:51,885 --> 00:05:53,452
Hey, you two...

91
00:05:53,453 --> 00:05:57,156
You said it, didn't you? "You are Number One!"

92
00:05:57,157 --> 00:05:58,991
Well, that was...

93
00:05:58,992 --> 00:06:01,026
Combat is a man's job!

94
00:06:01,027 --> 00:06:02,928
Talk about out of date!

95
00:06:02,929 --> 00:06:04,330
Unit 02 will back him up.

96
00:06:04,331 --> 00:06:06,351
Unit 00 will back him up as well.

97
00:06:07,167 --> 00:06:09,401
Damn kids, running with it...

98
00:06:09,402 --> 00:06:11,971
Shinji's gotten to be quite admirable, hasn't he?

99
00:06:11,972 --> 00:06:14,740
No, I'm going to have to chew him out
when he gets back.

100
00:06:14,741 --> 00:06:16,991
You'll make a good guardian.

101
